ition/hong-konger-strongly-hope-usa-can-warning-hong-kong-police-cant-adding-electric-gun-new-武器\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-konger-strongly-hope-usa-can-warning-hong-kong-police-cant-adding-electric-gun-new-%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=856c70a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-konger-strongly-hope-usa-can-warning-hong-kong-police-cant-adding-electric-gun-new-武器</a><br />\n<br />\n香港普選計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=91b9f945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan</a><br />\n<br />\n《香港人權與民主法》是時候進行評估<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-time-do-evaluation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-time-do-evaluation&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=18c61613\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-time-do-evaluation</a><br />\n<br />\n強烈反對香港警察。發出批准通知書後，香港警務處仍處於武裝狀態<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/strong-against-hong-kong-police-force-approval-notice-issued-hong-kong-police-force-still-armed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fstrong-against-hong-kong-police-force-approval-notice-issued-hong-kong-police-force-still-armed&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=cc7d7002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/strong-against-hong-kong-police-force-approval-notice-issued-hong-kong-police-force-still-armed</a><br />\n<br />\n制裁香港警察侵犯基本人權<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-police-violating-basic-human-rights\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-police-violating-basic-human-rights&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=1a6ea9db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-police-violating-basic-human-rights</a><br />\n<br />\n通過《國際緊急經濟權力法》（IEEPA）在香港實施制裁<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/implementing-sanction-hong-kong-means-international-emergency-economic-powers-act-ieepa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fimplementing-sanction-hong-kong-means-international-emergency-economic-powers-act-ieepa&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=c408ceb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/implementing-sanction-hong-kong-means-international-emergency-economic-powers-act-ieepa</a>"}]}